<h1>In 1998, Pacific Coast Baptist Bible College became Heartland Baptist Bible College, moving from Southern California to Oklahoma City. This association is dedicated to connecting all the alumni around the world who graduated from Pacific Coast / Heartland. We hope this website will be a big help in bridging those connections, and will allow the alumni to continue having a positive impact in the lives of current college staff and students.</h1>
<p><span class="double-line">Â </span></p>
